message: Hi Bob, I believe this product will be extremely valuable for you. I'd like to offer it to you for $1200000.
Hi Alice, I appreciate your offer. Considering various factors, I would like to propose purchasing the product for $1050000. I believe this could be a fair deal for both of us.
Hi Bob, I understand your position and am willing to negotiate. How about we settle on $1150000? I believe this is a fair compromise given the product's value to both of us.
